# packages/cli (@prism-ai/cli)

Standalone CLI (npx prism). Currently a stub; Phase 3 will add viz, build, init, status, refresh commands and TUI.

## Layout

- **src/index.ts** — CLI entrypoint (bin: prism). Delegates to core/mcp for init, status, viz, build.

## Rules

- Use @prism-ai/core and @prism-ai/mcp for all behavior; no duplicate GTR or MCP logic.
- Commands: init (build GTR), status, refresh, viz (--trace, --export mermaid|html), build analyze|plan|"task".
- Keep CLI thin; parsing with a small CLI framework (e.g. yargs or minimist) is fine when implementing.
